                Mr. Shakespeare
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-48461b5f-2b91-4edc-98f6-1e3118d3c399" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-03-17/debates/023c5cd6-c5de-40a4-870a-f97defe1072e/NavyEstimates1938#contribution-48461b5f-2b91-4edc-98f6-1e3118d3c399">
