    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the gratuities apply on the promotion of warrant officers to commissioned rank?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f65485dc-b6c8-48e0-a114-ee40ee91db28" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
