<div class="content-item" id="contribution-61bfdcfd-a725-499a-a9de-ecb4aea5b44e">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-61bfdcfd-a725-499a-a9de-ecb4aea5b44e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
